(122, '80301ce6-72f3-4898-9927-b90a21d4', 'service_highlight.email.fixed_content', '{\"heading\":\"Multiple Gateway Integration for Email Messaging\",\"btn_name\":\"Get Started\",\"btn_url\":\"http:\\/\\/localhost\\/xsender-revision\\/login\",\"description\":\"Maximize the reach and reliability of your email campaigns with XSender\'s multiple gateway integration. This feature allows you to connect with a variety of email gateways, such as SMTP, Mailjet, and others, providing flexibility and redundancy to ensure your messages are always delivered. By leveraging multiple gateways, you can distribute your email traffic efficiently, reduce the risk of delivery failures, and maintain high deliverability rates. XSender\'s multiple gateway integration empowers your business to handle large volumes of emails seamlessly, adapt to changing needs, and optimize your email marketing strategy for better engagement and results.\",\"service_highlight_image\":\"66863ab0a6d991720072880.webp\"}', 1, '2024-07-04 00:01:21', '2024-07-04 00:01:21'),
